Personally I did not like watching these movies the first time but after you get into the story it's better. However, some of the plot lines are just so dumb in #2 and especially #3... really have to turn a blind eye to logic. I have a suggestion to Bay and whomever else are doing these and the next 14 more to come: Ask yourself: What was John McClane do? (Bruce Willis in Die Hard.) And really, why not put Willis in one of these? I miss a real action hero.

I ordered this item because it stated that it was 3 movies in one set. When I received my package, I removed the plastic wrap just like every other movie you buy. When I opened the case, Transformers: Dark of the Moon was the only DVD in the case. While $10 isn't a lot for one movie, this item is misleading.
